    'test_promo_title': 'Test',
    'test_promo_definition': 'The history of the Great Patriotic War, like history as a whole, consists of facts. In this section of the site, you can test your knowledge by answering questions of various tests. We regularly add new tests to the site.',
    'title_remember': 'Belaruswar — We remember',
    'title_tests': 'Belaruswar — Tests',
    'defenition_promo_gallery': 'Photos of participants of the Great Patriotic War are collected in our archive. We regularly add new photos to the archive!',
    'defenition_promo_newspapers': 'Thanks to the military press, the Soviet soldiers raised their fighting spirit and they believed even more in the victory over the Nazi invaders.',
    'title_newspaper_block1': '«Bolshevik»',
    'title_newspaper_block2': '«War and the working class»',
    'defenition_block_radio': 'Every day of the Great Patriotic War, frontline correspondents collected information on the course of hostilities. Both Soviet soldiers and home front workers closely followed the news reports from the front. The Soviet Information Bureau was the main source of information.',
    'defenition_block_parads': 'Victory parades dedicated to the Great Patriotic War!',
    'defenition_block_letters': 'The letters of the war years preserve the memory of those days. They have everything: short stories about the war, poems, yellowed photos of soldiers, clippings from battle leaflets and newspapers, words of love for their loved ones and dreams of post-war happiness. In many families carefully, like relics, keep letters from parents and grandparents.',
    'defenition_block_gallery': 'Photos of participants in the Great Patriotic War are collected in our archive. We regularly add new photos to the archive!',
    'defenition_block_newspapers': 'Thanks to the military press, the fighting spirit of Soviet soldiers was raised and they believed even more in victory over the fascist invaders.',
    'defenition_remember_museum': 'The road to Victory was long and difficult - 1418 days and nights of this terrible war. Such incredible trials, torments and shocks fell to the lot of the Soviet people. How can you measure the long way to Victory? Grief, days, battles, suffering, courage, dedication? ... All these military events have entered our memory, our hearts, the life of the generation of the XXI century.',
    'text_about_site_third': 'We are patriots of our country! We will never forget the history of Belarus during the Great Patriotic War! Therefore, the purpose of creating the site belaruswar - to honor the memory of their grandfathers and great-grandfathers, who fought for the Motherland and at the cost of their lives won a VICTORY for us!',
    'text_about_site_second': 'The site has an archive with military documents, the section "Hero Cities", information about the Combat Glory Room of Gymnasium №7, a photo album and tests on the building of the history of the Great Patriotic War. Passing the tests, you will learn a lot about Belarus during the war, getting acquainted with the military archives, you will learn about your grandfathers, great-grandfathers who fought for our country! The Room of Military Glory is a museum exposition dedicated to young defenders of the Fatherland, which is located in the Gymnasium №7 of Minsk. The "Hero Cities" section will allow you to learn a lot about your city. The site is constantly updated with new interesting facts and materials.',
    'text_about_site_first': 'The project "Eternal Fire of Our Memory" is designed to educate the younger generation of citizenship, patriotism, respect for the history of their country, pride in the feat of their grandfathers and great-grandfathers.',
    'title_newspaper': 'Belaruswar — Newspapers',
    'title_promo_newspapers': 'Newspapers',
